Login Page:

Test Case 1:

Description: Verify successful login with valid credentials

Steps:

1) Enter a valid email address in the "Email" field.
2) Enter the correct password in the "Password" field.
3) Click the "Login" button.

 Expected Result:

User is successfully logged in and redirected to the appropriate page.

Test Case 2:

Description: Verify error message for invalid credentials

Steps:

1) Enter an invalid email address or password.
2) Click the "Login" button.

Expected Result:

An appropriate error message is displayed, indicating invalid credentials.


Test Case 3:

Description: Verify error message for empty fields

Steps:

1) Leave both email and password fields empty.
2) Click the "Login" button.

Expected Result:

Error messages are displayed for both missing fields.
